    "is_free": false,
    "description": "由一些《史蒂文宇宙：释放之光》的幕后人员创作，<strong>Ink Inside</strong>是一部手绘的冒险游戏，拥有周六早晨卡通的灵魂！<br><br>扮演未完成的素描Stick，被困在一堆笔记本箱下的漏水天花板下。随着水渗入笔记本，它扭曲了周围的土地，将曾经友好的涂鸦变成了无意识的、湿漉漉的怪物。通过抵御侵蚀世界的湿气浪潮，揭示失落的记忆并拯救你的朋友。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137880/extras/b8eb208dd656b3d9a9537197fd362bd3.poster.avif?t=1772134669\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137880/extras/b8eb208dd656b3d9a9537197fd362bd3.webm?t=1772134669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137880/extras/b8eb208dd656b3d9a9537197fd362bd3.mp4?t=1772134669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137880/extras/e1e1550b1681ff95d2aa3d3edfa68221.poster.avif?t=1772134669\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137880/extras/e1e1550b1681ff95d2aa3d3edfa68221.webm?t=1772134669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137880/extras/e1e1550b1681ff95d2aa3d3edfa68221.mp4?t=1772134669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>揭示Stick的遗传记忆或基因模因——每个素描与他们的创作者Hannah分享的记忆。探索素描本之间的世界，解锁记忆，结识完全配音和动画的生动角色。<br><br>由YouTube名人Brian David Gilbert（<i>辐射76</i>）和Deneen Melody（<i>新剧场版福音战士，刀剑神域</i>和Netflix的<i>浪漫杀手</i>）配音。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137880/extras/00299578c86f89891a70f9043fe1bd9f.poster.avif?t=1772134669\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137880/extras/00299578c86f89891a70f9043fe1bd9f.webm?t=1772134669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137880/extras/00299578c86f89891a70f9043fe1bd9f.mp4?t=1772134669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137880/extras/5f25cebc34c7686a4472e500da93ea12.poster.avif?t=1772134669\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137880/extras/5f25cebc34c7686a4472e500da93ea12.webm?t=1772134669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137880/extras/5f25cebc34c7686a4472e500da93ea12.mp4?t=1772134669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>遇见并招募一支多彩的角色团队来帮助你的旅程。从值得信赖的侦探Fuzz到像卡车一样打击和说话的咒语公主Traff。<br><br>揭开每个角色的故事，填补你自己历史的空白，深入感人的实景剧场景，并发现导致它们创造的遗传记忆。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137880/extras/99645fece76f74449c18728e244fb60e.poster.avif?t=1772134669\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137880/extras/99645fece76f74449c18728e244fb60e.webm?t=1772134669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137880/extras/99645fece76f74449c18728e244fb60e.mp4?t=1772134669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137880/extras/0b2494fce84b80fe717a9810b0df2da9.poster.avif?t=1772134669\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137880/extras/0b2494fce84b80fe717a9810b0df2da9.webm?t=1772134669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137880/extras/0b2494fce84b80fe717a9810b0df2da9.mp4?t=1772134669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在充满行动的躲避球与格斗风格的战斗中对抗敌人，你将躲避着弹道的图案，连击以逃脱粘糊糊的命运。<br><br>收集新装备，解锁更强大的能力，并填满你的酷炫动作条，通过击破保护敌人的无形壁来造成额外伤害。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137880/extras/bf4a190619b0b0142a405ca9d533ea97.poster.avif?t=1772134669\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137880/extras/bf4a190619b0b0142a405ca9d533ea97.webm?t=1772134669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137880/extras/bf4a190619b0b0142a405ca9d533ea97.mp4?t=1772134669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137880/extras/2b88c0e29b515445f321853c8560ee72.poster.avif?t=1772134669\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137880/extras/2b88c0e29b515445f321853c8560ee72.webm?t=1772134669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137880/extras/2b88c0e29b515445f321853c8560ee72.mp4?t=1772134669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>完成任务以揭示深层的传说，并探索广阔而绚丽的世界，从Fuzzball Forest到Sugar Swamp。<br><br>访问商店升级你的装备，升级并混搭新的机制，以帮助你在拯救公主的史诗般的任务中获得胜利。",
